To build isip you will need a C compiler and ragel.  To view the
state charts ragel produces (optional) you will need graphviz and a
PDF viewer.
    * ragel: http://www.complang.org/ragel/
    * graphviz (optional): http://www.graphviz.org/

make
make check
make install

You may want to set PREFIX to something like /usr, the default is
/usr/local.  Packagers may want to set DESTDIR.

PREFIX=/usr DESTDIR=../pkg make install
